{"tid":945392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手一年都放唔低 生活大壓力 諗唔通 有冇人可以開解下我","createTime":"2018-12-18T00:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T13:16:26.000Z","uid":189310,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e9b6a2ee9e43aebb17aef21324bbe4582cf4dad7","tid":945392,"uid":189310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"六月畢業，仲做緊廢青，幾次搵工都失敗。幫小學生補習都遇到怪獸家長俾人炒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢又無日日係屋企。<br />\n<br />\n同前男友上年一月分手，人哋都有穩定女朋友，我仲掛住人成日偷睇人哋啲嘢。係屋企嘅同佢嘢都唔捨得抌。重點係而家我自己都有對象，但就係同佢唔係咁開心，好唔自在。感覺自己都唔係真正鍾意佢，好似曬緊人地時間咁。好唔知足，想要更多。<br />\n<br />\n我到底可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到而家都瞓唔到 <br />\n啱啱仲諗起往事，默默地流淚。"},{"pid":"bce16f34ce6826d05c89b4285b622ecff173b899","tid":945392,"uid":64259,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"試下一無所有 好快起返身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大前提係你要有能力承擔後果"},{"pid":"fc62d9abd9438fdcf966f08e3e58b6ac8473bec9","tid":945392,"uid":189310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce16f34ce6826d05c89b4285b622ecff173b899","tid":945392,"uid":64259,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"試下一無所有 好快起返身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大前提係你要有能力承擔後果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T00:43:48.000Z","msg":"但係我而家已經冇錢 銀行得返700蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通All in咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff0a9111c47e0ae2fcc51402ce16e3fb5cbaf14","tid":945392,"uid":64259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc62d9abd9438fdcf966f08e3e58b6ac8473bec9","tid":945392,"uid":189310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce16f34ce6826d05c89b4285b622ecff173b899","tid":945392,"uid":64259,"like